LIVE DEMO SITE
──────────────
The live demo at https://msa-dev.fact-mine.com is provided free of charge
for personal and educational use. Data you create on the demo site is
stored only in your browser's localStorage and never transmitted to
external servers.

For commercial / on-premise / enterprise use, please contact via the demo
site or open an issue on this repository.

